</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="nt">&lt;span</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"clock"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></figure>

